CatDescriptText: Cutline of image published in Pittsburgh Courier newspaper, April 5, 1958, pg. 5 reads: "6. Lovely Sherlynn Dudley points out Meadow Gold Dairies buttermilk in their booth as Ronald Mitchell and George Shipley nod their aproval [sic]."
TitMainTitle: Sherlynn Dudley, standing between Ronald Mitchell and George Shipley in Meadow Gold Dairies booth in Syria Mosque for the 1958 Pittsburgh Courier Home Service Fair
